# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Models
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The ONNX weights are NOT redistributed in this repo:
#  - yolov4.onnx is too large for GitHub (>100 MB hard limit on a single file).
#  - YOLO26 weights are AGPL-3.0 (Ultralytics). Users fetch them via
#    station\scripts\download-models.ps1 (HF mirror) or export from .pt themselves.
# Match a Models/ folder at any depth (weights live in station/Models/ after the
# monorepo reorg; the leading **/ also keeps the legacy repo-root path ignored).
**/Models/*.onnx
**/Models/*.data
**/Models/*.CPU.onnx
**/Models/*.NPU.onnx
**/Models/*.GPU.onnx

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Per-script venv / temp artifacts
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# (download-models.ps1 creates its venv at %LOCALAPPDATA% so it's already outside the repo)
*.log
*.tmp

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OS clutter
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store

